### **4. 30_LiveMetricGrid**  
**Description:**  
Displays streaming numeric data in a grid-like live-updating chart with multi-series support.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveMetricGrid - Realtime Data Stream Visualizer

LiveMetricGrid lets you track and visualize multiple numeric data feeds in real-time with smooth chart updates.

## Features
- Multi-series live chart  
- Scrollable with time axis  
- Adjustable update speed  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/30_LiveMetricGrid.git
cd 30_LiveMetricGrid
python visualize.py
